title: **Below Market Rate** 1BR apt, High ceilings, Fully-equipped kitchen
posting_body: ['With 10-foot ceilings and much of the original woodwork and trim, each New Century Commons apartment home is different and special.', 'Your apartment may have the original built-in china cabinets with glass doors, a large bay window, or large cheerful skylights.', 'Every kitchen is totally modern, with dishwasher and built-in microwave oven.', 'This apartment features:', 'Below Market Rental (BMR)', '**', 'Special Income Restrictions Apply **', '** Call for Details **', 'Located in Historic Downtown San Jose area', 'Spacious rooms!', 'Close to the Light Rail', 'Large, bright skylight', 'High ceilings', 'Come Visit us!', 'New Century Commons', '56 S Second St', 'San Jose, CA 95113', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday – Friday9:00 am - 6:00 pm', 'Saturday9:00 am - 2:00 pm', 'Contact us to schedule a tour', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', "related search terms ::: downtown san jose, san jose, light rail, Light Rail, San Jose State University, MLK library, Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Library, San Jose Museum of Art, Tech Museum, Children's Discovery Museum, Bus lines,", 'San Jose Improv, Improv Comedy Club, SAP Center, Safeway, Local Store, A to Z Market']
